Section::::Belgian productions .
In 1978 , from 29 April to 10 June 1978 , the Belgian production of the Rocky Horror Show was staged at Teater Arena Ghent in Belgium , under the direction of Jaak Van de Velde .
The cast featured Daan Van den Durpel as Frank - N - Furter , Linda Lepomme as Janet , Marijn Devalck as Brad , Wim Huys as Riff - Raff , Carmen Jonckheere as Magenta / Usherette , Chris Thys as Columbia , Jakob Beks as Eddie
/ Dr .
Scott , Paul Codde as Rocky Horror , and Bert Van Tichelen as The Narrator .
The libretto was translated by Hugo Heinen and Rene Solleveld .
