Japan Cast AWARDS AND NOMINATIONS Section::::Awards and nominations .
The original London production won the award for Best Musical of 1973 at the Evening Standard Awards in January 1974 .
Additionally , both the original Broadway production and the 2000 revival of the musicals have accrued nominations for both Tony Awards and Drama Desk Awards .
